title: Tech falls to Mississippi State, 11-5 - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech falls to Mississippi State, 11-5 - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: BILOXI, Miss. – In the first of two games at MGM Park, No. 17 Texas Tech fell 11-5 to No. 23 Mississippi State on Tuesday night. The two programs square off at 5 p.m. Wednesday to wrap up the two-game midweek series.
